						               													<description>You and your Opponent have been rivals all through the Wizard Academy. It is now your final exam and the perfect opportunity to roast that guy once and for all.  The first to deal 20 damage wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Like any wizard duel it is a battle of wits to see who will come out on top.  Each player has a character card with special abilities and the same 6 spells, 2 defence, 2 offence and 2 utility.  Players choose a spell from their hand and place it face down in front of them.  Once both players have chosen, they turn them face up simultaneously and resolve the effects in Energy Number order.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;However if both spells have the same Energy Number then they are cancelled.  Too many cancelled spells in a round and the characters abilities come into play.  First they punish, then they get desperate and desperate people can do almost anything.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;link to the Work-in-Progress: http://www.boardgamegeek.com/article/19029697#19029697&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
